Section 1: Preamble
DMind is an open-source AGI research organization focused on next-generation digital finance. Driven by real market needs, DMind continuously releases open-source products—including large language models, benchmarks, datasets, tools, and more.

As an open, research-driven community, DMind is powered by a global collective of AI and Web3 enthusiasts, builders, and researchers. All of our work is released under permissive licenses, enabling individuals and enterprises alike to freely use, adapt, and build upon them to create new AI-native innovations.

DMind-2-4B is a crypto investment analysis large language model specifically optimized for edge deployment, enabling users to access institutional-grade investment analysis capabilities on local devices without concerns about data privacy or network latency. Built through innovative post-training techniques including Distribution-Preserving Chain-of-Thought Distillation (DPCD), the model achieves extreme lightweight while maintaining professional analysis capabilities. DMind-2-4B requires minimum 4GB VRAM and supports consumer-grade GPUs, making it ideal for individual investors seeking real-time crypto investment consulting. The model is derived from Qwen3-4B-Thinking-2507 and contains approximately 4B parameters.

This license is designed to enable open and responsible use of DMind-2-4B. It grants broad rights to use, modify, and redistribute the model, while also enforcing responsible-use provisions to prevent misuse.

